string.name: STR_CHAT_ROOM_HELP
string.body: /Create Channel: You can create a private channel by typing as follows: /Create Channel [channel name] [password]. You do not need to enter a password if you do not wish to set one. /Join Channel: You can enter a private channel by typing as follows: /Join Channel [channel name] [password]. You do not need to enter a password if none has been set for the channel. /Leave Channel: You can leave a private channel by typing as follows: /Leave Channel [channel name]. /Channel Member Info: You can see all characters in a private channel by typing as follows: /Channel Member Info [channel name]. /Channel Information: You can see the information of the private channel you are in by typing as follows: /Channel Information [channel name]. /Channel Ban Info: You can see a list of the characters expelled from a private channel by typing as follows: /Channel Ban Info [channel name]. /Ban from Channel: You can force a character to leave a private channel by typing as follows: /Ban from Channel [channel name] [character name]. Only the channel leader can use this function. /Unban from Channel: You can allow a character to rejoin a private channel by typing as follows: /Unban from Channel [channel name] [character name]. /Entrust Channel Leader Authority: You can entrust a character with the channel leader authority by typing as follows: /Entrust Channel Leader Authority [channel name] [character name]. Only the channel leader can use this function. /Change Channel Password: You can set a new channel password by typing as follows: /Change Channel Password [channel name] [password]. Only the channel leader can use this function. /Channel Help: You can see all commands available for the channel.

string.body: It cannot be created because either your Aion pass has expired or you do not meet the Free Wing Service requirements. The Free Wing Service offers three free characters for your account. If you have more than three characters, you can delete one to include a new character from the Free Wing Service. For unrestricted access to Aion, please buy a gameplay coupon.

string.name: STR_MSG_WOFS_CANT_ENTER_CHARACTER_OVER
string.body: You cannot access the game if your Aion pass has expired or you do not meet the Free Wing Service requirements. The Free Wing Service can be used for free for three characters in your account. If you have more than three characters, you can delete one to include a new character from the Free Wing Service. For unrestricted access to Aion, please buy a gameplay coupon.

string.name: STR_MSG_WOFS_CANT_ENTER_LEVEL_OVER
string.body: You cannot access the game if your Aion pass has expired or you do not meet the Free Wing Service requirements. The Free Wing Service offers free characters in your account that are level 45 and below. The Free Wing Service is also available to players who have deleted a character that is level 46 or higher. For unrestricted access to Aion, please buy a gameplay coupon.

string.name: STR_MSG_WOFS_CANT_ENTER_BOTH_OVER
string.body: You cannot access the game if your Aion pass has expired or you do not meet the Free Wing Service requirements. The Free Wing Service offers free wings to 3 characters in your account that are level 45 and below. The Free Wing Service is also available to players who have deleted a character that is level 46 or higher and have 3 characters or less in their account. For unrestricted access to Aion, please buy a gameplay coupon.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_UPGRADE_1_LEVEL
string.body:
You have been placed under Lv. 1 Probation due to reports regarding your automated hunting. The Lv. 1 Probation does not hinder your gameplay, but continued reports against you will result in restrictions to your in-game items and XP..
You can use the '/Propation' command to check your current Probation Phase.
Enter '%0' in the input window after you check the message.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_UPGRADE_2_LEVEL
string.body:
You have been placed under Lv. 2 Probation due to reports regarding your automated hunting. The Lv. 2 Probation lowers your XP, Kinah, and AP acquisition rates, and gathering and extraction success rates. Continued reports will lead to increased restrictions.
You can use the '/Probation' command to check your current Probation status.
Enter '%0' in the input window after you check the message.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_UPGRADE_3_LEVEL
string.body:
You have been placed under Lv. 3 Probation due to reports regarding your automated hunting. You now have severely limited XP, Kinah, AP, gatherable, and extracted item acquisition, and can no longer acquire loot. You can no longer join groups or alliances. You will face even greater restrictions should the reports continue to accumulate, increasing your Probation Lv. state even higher.
You can use the '/Probation' command to check your current Probation status.
Enter '%0' in the input window after you have checked the message.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_UPGRADE_4_LEVEL
string.body:
You have been placed under Lv. 4 Probation due to reports regarding your automated hunting. You can no longer acquire XP, Kinah, AP, gatherables, or extracted items, and can no longer join groups or alliance.
You can use the '/Probation' command to check your current Probation status.
Enter '%0' in the input window after you have checked the message.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_DEGRADE_LEVEL
string.body:
Your restriction phase has been lowered to %num0 as you played fair for a certain period of time. Please continue to play fair in the future.
You can use the 'Restriction' command to check your current Restriction Phase.

string.name: STR_ACCUSE_DEGRADE_NORMAL_LEVEL
string.body:
You returned to a normal state because you played fair for a certain period of time. Please continue to play fair in the future.
You can use the 'Restriction' command to check your current Restriction Phase.

string.name: STR_FATIGUE_UPGRADE_1_LEVEL
string.body:
You received Lv.1 Rest Recommendation because you have been playing for too long. While the Lv.1 Rest Recommendation is in effect, your rewards are halved.
For your health, please log out and take a rest.
You can use the '/RestRecommendation' command to check your Rest Recommendation Level.

string.name: STR_FATIGUE_UPGRADE_2_LEVEL
string.body:
You received Lv.2 Rest Recommendation because you have been playing for too long. While the Lv.2 Rest Recommendation is in effect, you cannot obtain rewards or trade items. Upon death, the character is teleported to a set resurrection point.
Please log out and take a break for your health.
You can use the '/RestRecommendation' command to check your Rest Recommendation Level.

string.name: STR_MSG_ACCUSE_INFO_3_LEVEL_BOT
string.body: You are in a Phase 3 Restriction State. You cannot acquire any loot, and your EXP, Kinah, and Abyss Point acquisition rates as well as gathering and extraction success rates are decreased significantly. You are also banned from joining a group or force. You will face even greater restrictions should you receive more reports, raising your Restriction Phase.

string.name: STR_MSG_ACCUSE_INFO_4_LEVEL_BOT
